"use strict";(globalThis.webpackChunkwebsite=globalThis.webpackChunkwebsite||[]).push([[792],{9935(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"v4-6-0-released","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/v4-6-0-released","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/tree/main/website/blog/2026-01-16-v4-6-0-released.md","source":"@site/blog/2026-01-16-v4-6-0-released.md","title":"v4.6.0 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.0 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, uzun zamand\u0131r beklenen VIP Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc, geli\u015fmi\u015f rota y\xf6netimi ve esnek fiyatland\u0131rma motoru gibi b\xfcy\xfck \xf6zellikler i\xe7eriyor.","date":"2026-01-16T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"v4.6.0","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/tags/v-4-6-0"},{"inline":true,"label":"vip-transfer","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/tags/vip-transfer"}],"readingTime":1.17,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4-6-0-released","title":"v4.6.0 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","v4.6.0","vip-transfer"],"date":"2026-01-16T00:00:00.000Z"},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"v4.5.5 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/v4-5-5-released"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.6.0** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, uzun zamand\u0131r beklenen **VIP Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc**, geli\u015fmi\u015f rota y\xf6netimi ve esnek fiyatland\u0131rma motoru gibi b\xfcy\xfck \xf6zellikler i\xe7eriyor.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83c\udf1f \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kanlar\\n\\n### \ud83d\ude80 VIP Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc (\u015eof\xf6rl\xfc Hizmet)\\nArt\u0131k sadece ara\xe7 kiralama de\u011fil, **VIP Transfer** hizmeti de verebilirsiniz!\\n- **Noktadan Noktaya Transfer:** Belirli lokasyonlar aras\u0131nda sabit veya mesafeye dayal\u0131 fiyatland\u0131rma.\\n- **\u015eof\xf6rl\xfc Ara\xe7 Kiralama:** Saatlik veya g\xfcnl\xfck \u015fof\xf6rl\xfc ara\xe7 opsiyonlar\u0131.\\n- **Ekstra Hizmetler:** Kar\u015f\u0131lama, bebek koltu\u011fu, ikramlar gibi ekstralar.\\n\\n### \ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f Rota ve Lokasyon Y\xf6netimi\\nAdmin panelinden detayl\u0131 **Rota Y\xf6netimi** yapabilirsiniz.\\n- Kalk\u0131\u015f ve Var\u0131\u015f noktalar\u0131 i\xe7in \xf6zel fiyatlar tan\u0131mlay\u0131n.\\n- \u0130ki nokta aras\u0131ndaki mesafeyi ve s\xfcreyi otomatik hesaplay\u0131n veya manuel girin.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udcb0 Esnek Fiyatland\u0131rma Motoru\\nTransferler i\xe7in geli\u015fmi\u015f fiyatland\u0131rma se\xe7enekleri:\\n- **Sabit Fiyat:** \\"Havaliman\u0131 -> \u015eehir Merkezi: 500 TL\\" gibi sabit rotalar olu\u015fturun.\\n- **Mesafe Bazl\u0131:** KM ba\u015f\u0131na \xfccretlendirme ile dinamik fiyatlar hesaplay\u0131n.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd0d Geli\u015fmi\u015f Transfer Arama\\nYeni **`[mhm_rentiva_transfer_search]`** k\u0131sa kodu ile web sitenize profesyonel bir transfer arama motoru ekleyin.\\n- Tarih, saat, kalk\u0131\u015f ve var\u0131\u015f noktas\u0131 se\xe7imi.\\n- Yolcu say\u0131s\u0131 ve bagaj kapasitesine g\xf6re ara\xe7 filtreleme.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Operasyonel Kontrol (Buffer Time)\\nAra\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131n temizli\u011fi ve haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in iki rezervasyon aras\u0131na otomatik **Tampon S\xfcre (Buffer Time)** ekleyebilirsiniz. Art\u0131k ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131n \\"M\xfcsait\\" durumu daha ger\xe7ek\xe7i y\xf6netiliyor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f D\xfczeltmeler ve \u0130yile\u015ftirmeler\\n\\n- **Cart & Payment:** WooCommerce sepet entegrasyonu \\"Depozito\\" veya \\"Tam \xd6deme\\" se\xe7enekleriyle g\xfc\xe7lendirildi.\\n- **Data Integrity:** Transfer detaylar\u0131 (kalk\u0131\u015f/var\u0131\u015f, yolcu say\u0131s\u0131) art\u0131k sipari\u015f notlar\u0131na ve meta verilerine eksiksiz kaydediliyor.\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Nas\u0131l G\xfcncellerim?**\\nWordPress panelinizden otomatik g\xfcncelleme yapabilirsiniz. Herhangi bir sorun ya\u015farsan\u0131z l\xfctfen GitHub \xfczerinden veya destek sayfam\u0131zdan bize ula\u015f\u0131n.\\n\\nKeyifli s\xfcr\xfc\u015fler! \ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83d\udca8"},{"id":"v4-5-5-released","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/v4-5-5-released","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/tree/main/website/blog/2026-01-15-v4-5-5-released.md","source":"@site/blog/2026-01-15-v4-5-5-released.md","title":"v4.5.5 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.5.5 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, kararl\u0131l\u0131k iyile\u015ftirmeleri, kritik performans d\xfczeltmeleri ve dok\xfcmantasyon altyap\u0131s\u0131nda b\xfcy\xfck yenilikler i\xe7eriyor.","date":"2026-01-15T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"v4.5.5","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/tags/v-4-5-5"}],"readingTime":0.64,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4-5-5-released","title":"v4.5.5 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","v4.5.5"],"date":"2026-01-15T00:00:00.000Z"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"v4.6.0 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/blog/v4-6-0-released"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.5.5** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, kararl\u0131l\u0131k iyile\u015ftirmeleri, kritik performans d\xfczeltmeleri ve dok\xfcmantasyon altyap\u0131s\u0131nda b\xfcy\xfck yenilikler i\xe7eriyor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83c\udf1f \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kanlar\\n\\n*   **G\xfcvenlik & Mimari:** Plugin kaynak kodlar\u0131 art\u0131k Private bir repoda korunurken, dok\xfcmantasyon (bu site) Public bir repoda herkesin eri\u015fimine a\xe7\u0131k hale getirildi.\\n*   **Performans:** Raporlama mod\xfcl\xfcndeki SQL sorgular\u0131, `DATE()` fonksiyonu kald\u0131r\u0131larak indeks kullan\u0131m\u0131na uygun hale getirildi. Art\u0131k \xe7ok daha h\u0131zl\u0131 \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor.\\n*   **Mobil Uyumluluk:** Ara\xe7 detay sayfalar\u0131 mobilde art\u0131k ta\u015fma yapm\u0131yor, butonlar ve g\xf6rseller tam uyumlu.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f D\xfczeltmeler\\n\\n*   **Fixed:** `Plugin.php` i\xe7indeki m\xfckerrer kodlar temizlendi.\\n*   **Fixed:** `ReportRepository` s\u0131n\u0131f\u0131ndaki yava\u015f sorgular optimize edildi.\\n*   **Fixed:** Ara\xe7 k\u0131yaslama sayfas\u0131ndaki hizalama sorunlar\u0131 giderildi.\\n*   **Fixed:** \\"Hizmete Kapal\u0131\\" (Out of Use) etiketi art\u0131k varyasyonlu \xfcr\xfcnlerde de do\u011fru \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce6 Y\xfckseltme\\n\\nWordPress panelinizden otomatik g\xfcncelleme yapabilirsiniz. Herhangi bir sorun ya\u015farsan\u0131z l\xfctfen GitHub \xfczerinden veya destek sayfam\u0131zdan bize ula\u015f\u0131n.\\n\\nKeyifli kiralamalar! \ud83d\ude97\ud83d\udca8"}]}}')}}]);